				<ANNOTATION_VALUE>ikh hob mayne oyfgabn oysgefirt. ikh fleg farkoyfn kleyninke fotokartishkes bay mayne khaveyrim, bay mayne bakante, shkheynim,</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
